N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 465.5 - Hours

State Regulations

Requests for access to case files shall be accepted and
files produced between 9 a.m. and 4 p.m. on regular business days on which the

Department of Labor offices are open. Notes
